column10: @Bryan675 Finally had time to breathe. Glad I can lend a voice (and hashtag #girlslikeus) to Jenna's plight.
@MSKLARZ Someone reached out to me a few months back. I'll have to join on a Tuesday in the summer when work slows down. #girlslikeus
@ashlee5582 If we don't speak up and support #girlslikeus, no one will. Thanks for using the hashtag and lending your voice!
@janetmock absolutely girl! Thanks for being a true inspiration to us all! #girlslikeus
RT @janetmock: There are currently 34,849 (out of 35,000) signatures supporting Jenna Talackova and #girlslikeus: http://t.co/uehSm6aQ
@dinadelicious Ditto! If we don't fight for her and #girlslikeus, who will? Just gotta put some Kevyn Aucoin on my bags in the AM. ;-)
